Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:04.53,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}悲しみ連鎖の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:04.53,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在悲傷的連鎖之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.72,0:00:14.17,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}僕らの願いが届くまで…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.72,0:00:14.17,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在我們的願望實現之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:23.06,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}大事なものまた一つ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:23.06,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}又一件珍貴的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.61,0:00:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,0)\fs48}戰場女武神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:27.68,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}モノクロの空へと消える
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:27.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}消失在黑白的空中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.14,0:00:34.47,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}隠したキズ冷たく震え
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.14,0:00:34.47,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}隱藏的傷痕在發冷顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.91,0:00:38.85,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}自分の居場所を探す
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.91,0:00:38.85,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}去找尋我的容身之處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.21,0:00:46.66,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}常識に従うこの世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.21,0:00:46.66,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在這個遵循常識的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.74,0:00:51.38,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}どうしようもできないことを
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.74,0:00:51.38,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}想打破無可救藥的桎梏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.23,0:00:55.58,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}壊していきたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.23,0:00:55.58,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}按自己的意志自由生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.65,0:01:03.13,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}閉ざしたココロ叫んでいる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.65,0:01:03.13,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}封閉的心靈正發出吶喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.02,0:01:10.58,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}悲しみ連鎖の中で僕らは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.02,0:01:10.58,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在悲傷的連鎖之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.68,0:01:16.22,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}自分さえも見失いそうになって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.68,0:01:16.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我們幾乎快要迷失自我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:20.15,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}曖昧な答えはイラナイ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:20.15,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}不需要曖昧的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.25,0:01:26.66,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}確かな今　追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.25,0:01:26.66,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}只需去追尋真切的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.66,0:01:38.16,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,400)}果てなく續く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.78,0:01:36.29,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(660,715)\fad(500,0)\4a&HFF\t(100,500,\4a&H80)\t(4090,4490,\4a&HFF)}精靈節的饋贈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,0:01:57.63,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,400)}光は強く明日を照らす　胸の…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 路過聽到聲音而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.31,0:02:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.31,0:02:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才唱得是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.18,0:02:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念遠方故鄉的達魯庫斯歌謠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.94,0:02:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是達魯庫斯的人偶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 想把它作為精靈節的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.37,0:02:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 給誰的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.62,0:02:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧你想得出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.70,0:02:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精靈節送什麼禮物 我們又不是孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.25,0:02:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向平日裡照顧自己的人和身邊人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.56,0:02:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表達謝意 是件好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是這麼說 送給誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.59,0:02:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是哥哥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算送給哥哥的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.68,0:02:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布魯魯和蘭蒂格瑞絲也能看到同樣的月亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.38,0:03:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 抱歉說些奇怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.95,0:03:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.77,0:03:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪魯貝利海岸？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次奉命執行的作戰行動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.91,0:03:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是殲滅那裡的帝國軍防禦陣地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為殲滅敵人基地 必須穿過空曠的海岸地帶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人佈陣於峭壁間的山坡上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩旁有堅固的碉堡群
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.85,0:03:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於無處藏身 進攻方將處於壓倒性劣勢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自始至終暴露在敵人炮火下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.51,0:03:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有跡象表明敵人打算從那裡攻打加利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選擇此時進攻的意義究竟何在…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:04:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達蒙將軍打算讓第七小隊充當先鋒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.41,0:04:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正規軍呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能會視義勇軍的作戰進展情況而定…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.44,0:04:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我去向隊員說明嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這是隊長的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.06,0:04:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.21,0:04:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞏特爾少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉聲歎氣會影響士氣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.61,0:04:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞏特爾少尉 剛才把補缺目錄放在你桌上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請過目
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.16,0:04:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.23,0:04:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬧彆扭？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…你怎麼會來這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.84,0:04:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你看看也無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.95,0:05:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近博格宰相和達蒙將軍接觸頻繁 聽說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達蒙將軍方面有可疑舉動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來已經發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.26,0:05:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上個月在蘭蒂格瑞絲城的事 我還記得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.81,0:05:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博格宰相 軍功章 達蒙將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上能讓人聯想到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃利特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願我的忠告是多此一舉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 埃利特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.54,0:05:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.52,0:05:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉不是艾麗西婭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.02,0:06:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽帕羅特女士說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.45,0:06:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們成了別人的眼中釘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…不是軍隊的機密文件嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.67,0:06:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼機密
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本入不了他們的法眼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就借來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.04,0:06:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加利亞北部戰線出現神秘的青色發光現象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正規軍第五中隊損失慘重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.88,0:06:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起什麼瑪魯貝利 他們應該多關心這些才對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上就是作戰情況說明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 精靈節也要去打仗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天不能外出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是全家團聚的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.63,0:06:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭不會顧及這些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請忘記精靈節吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 全都是我的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣 維爾金總是動不動就道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長能這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.69,0:07:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 得到勳章得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.22,0:07:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅茜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義勇軍不自量力去接受什麼勳章 所以被人盯上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.79,0:07:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說 羅茜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是對方說要頒發的 隊長有什麼過錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.63,0:07:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長大人好出風頭招致反感 使我們成為眾矢之的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅茜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是達蒙將軍用心險惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.60,0:07:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 隊長沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能向帝國和達蒙屈服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭也高興點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.68,0:08:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生氣會生皺紋的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.47,0:08:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.16,0:08:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅茜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.74,0:08:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要感謝我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為羅茜小姐的話 哥哥才沒有成為惡人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你誤會了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是說真心話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣行不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.51,0:08:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種小隊裡 到時候怎麼死的都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.27,0:08:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.38,0:08:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓任何人死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃米爾 畫啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第七小隊的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是精靈節
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想空著手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.94,0:09:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮物？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.97,0:09:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我送給維爾金？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…畢竟是隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是兩碼事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夫妻吵架？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 我可辛苦了 又沒時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.73,0:09:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顧不了什麼精靈節
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法爾迪奧也會安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維爾金也是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要烤焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.61,0:10:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燙傷了嗎 好嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須馬上處理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.88,0:10:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 法爾迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上回也烤焦了一鍋麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又燙傷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.64,0:10:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒臉自稱大師級別了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多泡一會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 我說過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.75,0:10:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這人傷好得特別快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點擔心柴火 得去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過會見 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.09,0:11:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成是在做精靈節的禮物？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能替我保密嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我保證
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不想告訴任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡顧著自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哥哥的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.77,0:12:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在維爾金面前太撒嬌了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是得認清自己的身份與他相處
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.45,0:12:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭怎麼看待哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼看待？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.11,0:12:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說了那種話 但我認為他是個好隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.70,0:12:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥看起來稱職 是因為他一心想做好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從父親死後 哥哥時常顯得不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭 請不要討厭哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.53,0:12:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請收下 打開看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不快收下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊迪…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精靈節快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.55,0:13:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精靈節快樂 法爾迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.70,0:13:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快好了 看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭的父母也是這種體質嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.96,0:13:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 我從小在孤兒院長大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是那塊救了我的Ragnite吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你重新收下它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.41,0:14:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送你的 因為是精靈節
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.65,0:14:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都沒準備
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 你的那份送出去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.58,0:14:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要送哦 說好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.94,0:14:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.31,0:14:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.63,0:14:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有海流的影響吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎整天都這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整天…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這裡有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.85,0:15:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有東西想給哥哥看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙霧彈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過改良 延長了在空中滯留的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.35,0:15:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那種風勢下 不知有多大效果…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪魯貝利海岸看似整日暴露在強風中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上朝夕各有一小時 處於無風狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.44,0:15:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是最好的攻擊時機
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙霧彈發射的同時全員突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由Edelweiss號摧毀敵人碉堡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.19,0:15:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵達暗礁地帶後 由步兵繼續突入
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會這麼順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深更半夜偷偷摸摸 原來在做這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎  我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.12,0:15:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 考慮到不能保證完成…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒敢告訴大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒能完成 我們就會變成交叉火力下的靶子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅茜 少說幾句
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該感謝伊莎拉才對 而不是挖苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅茜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精靈節的禮物 雖然遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.34,0:16:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達魯庫斯自古相傳的護身符
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.74,0:16:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能逢凶化吉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要給我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送給模範哥哥不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 羅茜是突擊時的先鋒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:17:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它保佑了羅茜 也就保佑了第七小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張嘴比你哥哥甜多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.18,0:17:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莎拉 準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.03,0:17:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.64,0:17:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 煙霧彈發射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.38,0:17:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算借煙霧掩護接近嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:17:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別怕 敵人看不見我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.02,0:17:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.04,0:18:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙霧有增無減
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽聲音 朝敵人炮火聲的方向射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.35,0:18:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們無法行動反而不利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出動士兵 主動迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 有人在也說一聲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.37,0:18:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1點方向敵人據點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.27,0:18:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突擊時拜託掩護
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.08,0:18:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅茜 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是為了拾它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.97,0:19:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就被爆頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅茜 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.52,0:19:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅茜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.02,0:19:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.24,0:19:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託別在人耳邊扯著嗓門喊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.34,0:19:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家加把油 跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.64,0:19:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.47,0:19:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅茜和伊莎拉在這裡待命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.96,0:19:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的人跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.00,0:19:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.98,0:19:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.69,0:19:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬小心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.13,0:19:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.47,0:19:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:19:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別退縮 給我不停地開火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.77,0:20:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 基地受到加利亞軍兩面夾擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.59,0:20:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退 給我撤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.99,0:20:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來還算順利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅茜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.69,0:20:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷勢不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.91,0:20:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧這個護身符
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.14,0:21:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.87,0:21:46.11,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}悲しすぎる瞳が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.87,0:21:46.11,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}太過悲傷的眼眸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:52.78,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}この空を映す
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:52.78,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}映照出這片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.15,0:22:01.17,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}掛ける言葉がわからずに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.15,0:22:01.17,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}不知該說什麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.45,0:22:07.02,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}ただ　星を数えた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.45,0:22:07.02,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}只默默數著星星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.54,0:22:12.74,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}孤独で居る世界は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.54,0:22:12.74,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}孤獨的世界
